<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hammata Islands</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Hammata Islands</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        O excursie de toata ziua catre Insulele Qulaan, localizata in sudul Parcului National Wadi El-Hamata.
        Plecarea dupa micul dejun din Hamata Marina (din Marsa Alam 105 km) pe barca.
        Doua pauze de snorkeling (45 min) in jurul insulelor, sa poti admira frumusetea naturii nedescoperita inca .Acolo întâlnim si
        Insula cu frumoasa apa albastra si nisip alb ca din Caraibe! Pranzul va fi pe barca iar bauturile non alcoolice sunt incluse.
        Echipamentul de snorkeling (masca,tub,inotatoare) sunt incluse .
        Sosirea la hotel în jurul orelor 18:00-19:00
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        marti si miercuri
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A whole day excursion to Qulaan Islands, placed on the southern part of National Park Wadi El-Hamata. 
        Departure after breakfast from Hamata Marina (from Marsa Alam 105km) on the boat. 2 snorkleing breaks 
        (45min) around the islands to admire beauty of nature undiscovered yet by mass tourism. Islands with 
        beautifull blue water and white sands like from Carraibean! Lunch on the boat and non alcoholic drinks 
        included. Snorkeling equipment (mask,pipe,feence) available for free. Arrival to hotel at 18:00-19:00.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Tuesday, Wednesday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>